    "Id": "528514",
    "ThreadId": "236442",
    "Html": "\r\n<p><strong>ANSWER</strong></p>\r\n<p>I changed my config to the following, and it appears to be working now.&nbsp; Ten Thumbs Up for CHIRPY!!!</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div style=\"color:black; background-color:white\">\r\n<pre><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;?</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">xml</span> <span style=\"color:red\">version</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">1.0</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:red\">encoding</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">utf-8</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">?&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">root</span> <span style=\"color:red\">xmlns</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">urn:ChirpyConfig</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span>\r\n      <span style=\"color:red\">xmlns:xsi</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span>\r\n      <span style=\"color:red\">xsi:schemaLocation</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">urn:ChirpyConfig http://www.weirdlover.com/chirpy/chirp.xsd</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n    <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">FileGroup</span> <span style=\"color:red\">Name</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">site.js</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n        <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">File</span> <span style=\"color:red\">Path</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">jquery-ui-1.8.4.custom.min.js</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:red\">Minify</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">false</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">/&gt;</span>\r\n        <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">File</span> <span style=\"color:red\">Path</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">un-master.js</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">/&gt;</span>\r\n        <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">File</span> <span style=\"color:red\">Path</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">jquery-ui-timepicker-addon.min.js</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:red\">Minify</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">false</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">/&gt;</span>\r\n        <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">File</span> <span style=\"color:red\">Path</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">jquery-nmcFormHelper.js</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">/&gt;</span>\r\n        <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">File</span> <span style=\"color:red\">Path</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">jquery.textarearesizer.min.js</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:red\">Minify</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">false</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">/&gt;</span>\r\n        <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">File</span> <span style=\"color:red\">Path</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">jquery-openid.js</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">/&gt;</span>\r\n        <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">File</span> <span style=\"color:red\">Path</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">jquery.timeago.js</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">/&gt;</span>\r\n    <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">FileGroup</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">root</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n",
